attributes.action: Stop Sale of White Cliffs of Dover and Port
attributes.action_prefix: We the undersigned petition the Prime Minister to
attributes.background:
These White Cliffs and the Port are part of our national heritage and must stay British (could even make them Seven Wonders of the World,
They are set in stone by Dame Dera Lynn's song White Cliffs of Dover sung during the 2nd World War.Port used by our servicemen and Women when having to set forth into Battle.
I call on the French to keep their hands off and our PM? to get his Act together!!NOT FOR SALE

reasons: Duplicate - this is similar to and/or overlaps with an existing petition or petitions
